msItem.title: The posthumous works of the celebrated Dr. Sterne, deceased author of the Sentimental journey
Posthumous works of a late celebrated genius
msItem.note: First published as 'The posthumous works of a late celebrated genius deceased'; also published with the title 'The Koran; or, the life, character, and sentiments of Tria Juncta in Uno'.
An imitation of Sterne by Richard Griffith; sometimes attributed to Griffith's son, Richard Griffith.
